value-string:
The ways to get EXP include killing monsters, completing tasks, etc.
You can get a lot of EXP every time you complete a round of bounty missions.

You can buy LNCO through curve or crypto exchanges.
You can also get LNCO by selling game items in the marketplace.

Crafting weapon power, equipment power, and potions all increase the proficiency of the corresponding crafting skill.
The higher the level of crafting the item, the more the increased proficiency.
